data.description: Move-In Ready Wilson Semi        Nestled in a quiet neighborhood on a great lot with a private backyard is a move-in ready home with several upgrades and new paint throughout! Boasting the curb appeal of a new front door, newer roof, brick and vinyl facade, and covered front porch, this semi only gets better inside!  Upon entry, you’re immediately greeted by the bright and open living room with new flooring, double front window, and oversized doorway to the large dining area. A seamless flow to the kitchen makes entertaining easy, while glass slider doors to the awesome composite deck allows you to take hosting outside in the warmer seasons.  The chef in the family will love the updated kitchen with a nice island offering an eat-on option, new granite countertops, newer appliances, ceiling fan, and access to the laundry room with new cabinets and the powder room.  The Master bedroom enjoys a walk-in closet, carpeting, and an updated, private bathroom with tub/shower and tile flooring. Down the hall are two additional bedrooms with carpeting and an updated tile bathroom with a tub/shower.  Downstairs, the lower level has both a family room with newer flooring and a full utility room with tons of storage.  Enjoy any season on the large back deck as you admire your peaceful surroundings and wooded backdrop where friendly deer, rabbits, and more love to stop by to say hello.
